    aSCPrompt += 'If the redundancy filter is enabled, the algorithm then computes information gain: it ranks features by the extra ';
    aSCPrompt += 'information each adds beyond those already selected, ensuring multiple highly correlated variables are not picked ';
    aSCPrompt += 'for predictive model training. ';
    
    aSCPrompt += 'Practically, Signals help you identify and prioritize which sensor streams, process parameters, or categorical tags ';
    aSCPrompt += 'really drive your outcomewhether thats machine failure, product defect, or throughput variance. By focusing on top ';
    aSCPrompt += 'signals, you can streamline feature sets, reduce model complexity, and improve training performance and ';
    aSCPrompt += 'interpretability in subsequent predictive models. For manufacturers, this means turning terabytes of vibration, ';
    aSCPrompt += 'temperature, and operational logs into a concise list of actionable predictors that feed both dashboards and alerting ';
    aSCPrompt += 'workflows. ';
    
    aSCPrompt += 'Signals results can help give recommendations how to achive an objective with repsect to the goal variable. ';
